{"questionId":"11873","questionHtml":"<p>Find the exact values of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{0}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{1}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{0\\,}}{\\text{ = }}\\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {1\\,dx}&nbsp; = \\left[ x \\right]_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} = \\frac{\\pi }{4}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;=&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>[</mo>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>]</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>π</mi>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{1\\,}}{\\text{ = }}\\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {{\\text{tan}}\\,dx}&nbsp; = \\left[ { -